# ts-rs writes generated TypeScript bindings with LF line endings.
# On Windows, git's autocrlf would otherwise check them out as CRLF,
# `cargo test export_bindings` would regenerate them as LF, and the
# CI step that verifies bindings-vs-committed would diff every line.
# Force LF for the entire generated tree to keep CI deterministic.
src/lib/types/generated/** text eol=lf
